      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    P@PAS
     C                     CALL 'ABMR1B'
     C                     PARM           L6SHN1
     C                     PARM           L6SHN2
     C                     PARM           L6SHN3
     C                     PARM           P@PAS   1
      *
     C                     Z-ADDL6SYOS    @BSSYS
